The paper deals with mining attribute associations in graphs, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of social networks (cs.SI), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), databases (cs.DB), machine learning (cs.LG), and statistical analysis (cs.SD). However, since the focus is on finding statistically significant associations, cs.SI and cs.SD are the most likely sub-categories.
